                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-4 col-12 mt-4">
            <div class="row">
              <div class="col-lg4 col-md-4 col-12">
                <figure class="">
                  <img
                    src="images/prevent/home.png"
                    class="img-fluid float-left"
                    width="90"
                    height="90"
                    alt="logo"
                  />
                </figure>
              </div>

              <div class="col-lg-8 col-md-8 col-12">
                <p>
                  Stay home and self- isolate from others in the household if
                  you fell unwell.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-4 col-12 mt-4">
            <div class="row">
              <div class="col-lg4 col-md-4 col-12">
                <figure class="">
                  <img
                    src="images/prevent/ill.png"
                    class="img-fluid float-left"
                    width="90"
                    height="90"
                    alt="logo"
                  />
                </figure>
              </div>

              <div class="col-lg-8 col-md-8 col-12">
                <p>
                  If you have fiver, cough and difficulty breathing. seek
                  medical care early
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-4 col-12 mt-4">
            <div class="row">
              <div class="col-lg4 col-md-4 col-12">
                <figure class="">
                  <img
                    src="images/prevent/news.png"
                    class="img-fluid float-left"
                    width="90"
                    height="90"
                    alt="logo"
                  />
                </figure>
              </div>

              <div class="col-lg-8 col-md-8 col-12">
                <p>
                  Stay informed by wachting news and follow the recommended
                  practices.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
